title: 12/21/20 HOUR 3- Jeff Monken and Hank Azaria
itunes:title: 12/21/20 HOUR 3- Jeff Monken and Hank Azaria
description:
Jeff Monken tells Dan about some of his autograph attempts stories. Jeff says it was hard to believe that his Army team is not in a bowl game. Hank Azaria says that he is hurt emotionally that the Jets won against the Rams, because now they wont get the number 1 pick in the draft.
